@ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5146
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_AUTH_LOGIN

### List protocols
GET {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/protocols?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List protocols by status / phase
GET {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/protocols?status=Active&phase=Phase2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get protocol by id
GET {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/protocols/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create protocol (Admin / ClinicalTrialManager)
POST {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/protocols
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "LT-001 Cardio Outcomes Study",
  "phase": "Phase2",
  "startDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2027-12-31T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "Draft"
}

### Update protocol
PUT {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/protocols/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "LT-001 Cardio Outcomes Study (Amended)",
  "phase": "Phase2",
  "startDate": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2028-06-30T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "Active"
}

### Soft-delete protocol (Admin)
DELETE {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/protocols/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List sites
GET {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List sites filtered by investigator
GET {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites?investigatorId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get site by id
GET {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create site (Admin / ClinicalTrialManager)
POST {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Boston General Hospital",
  "location": "Boston, MA, USA",
  "investigatorId": null,
  "status": "Pending"
}

### Update site
PUT {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Boston General Hospital",
  "location": "55 Fruit St, Boston, MA",
  "investigatorId": 2,
  "status": "Active"
}

### Assign investigator
POST {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites/1/assign-investigator
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "investigatorId": 2
}

### Clear investigator assignment
POST {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites/1/assign-investigator
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "investigatorId": null
}

### Soft-delete site (Admin)
DELETE {{ProtocolSite.API_HostAddress}}/api/sites/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
